    "description": "You play as a young woman living in the slums of an industrial complex.<br>The ruling caste of the complex takes people from each district of the slums for all sorts of experimentation. This is the heavy price paid by the people living around the complex.<br><br>During one of these raids, she and others revolted and refused to give themselves up.<br>This led to their deaths and the purge of their district.<br>Although dead, a voice was heard. A dark entity made an offer: Life and vengeance for bloodshed.<br><br>Now she’s ready, and she has nothing to fear anymore …<br>Her only goal: <strong>Make them bleed</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/a3699207beaef5fc809ec2c97f017433.poster.avif?t=1740331630\" width=670 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/a3699207beaef5fc809ec2c97f017433.webm?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/a3699207beaef5fc809ec2c97f017433.mp4?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><u><i>Several powers are at his disposal:</i></u><br><br><strong>The rewind </strong>→ Instead of dying, go back 3 seconds in time <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/cd1fb10f6ca2f6fa1560e309e7e3f12c.poster.avif?t=1740331630\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/cd1fb10f6ca2f6fa1560e309e7e3f12c.webm?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/cd1fb10f6ca2f6fa1560e309e7e3f12c.mp4?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The dash </strong>→ What's better than a dash to get out of a bad situation?  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/19099a1f4f162779075aa37139809715.poster.avif?t=1740331630\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/19099a1f4f162779075aa37139809715.webm?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/19099a1f4f162779075aa37139809715.mp4?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Killing spree</strong>: After three kills, the entity's mark awakens, and you can now see enemies through walls and dash into them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/8ffe3c9bb36765741aeff646ebc76f68.poster.avif?t=1740331630\" width=670 height=377 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/8ffe3c9bb36765741aeff646ebc76f68.webm?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>A variety of <strong>weapons </strong>to suit your approach. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/06ce022252a4327554dedfa54db6740d.poster.avif?t=1740331630\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/06ce022252a4327554dedfa54db6740d.webm?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013570/extras/06ce022252a4327554dedfa54db6740d.mp4?t=1740331630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><u>It's all about speed: </u></strong><br>A global leaderboard : the 13 best times per level are recorded, so it's up to you to be among the 13.<br><br><strong><u>Abyssal Echoes:</u></strong><br>Complete the challenges on each level (No rewind / No shooting / Time attack / Killing spree), and unlock the Memories of the abyss. Shorter, more dangerous and more frenetic levels that reveal more about the entity…",
